This is the README file for XML::API::WIX2

INSTALLATION
XML::API::WIX2 uses the standard perl module install process
This module requires
XML::API
WiX (Windows Installer XML) version 2

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test [TEST_VERBOSE=1] (optional but recommended)
make install

DESCRIPTION
################################################################################
XML::API::WIX2 extends XML::API providing the ability to create Windows
Installer XML source files for use with Version 2 of WiX

The WiX (Windows Installer XML) Toolset can be obtained from
http://wix.sourceforge.net

